*&quot;Stenoonops&quot; — North America, Central America, Caribbean, South America, Seychelles
*&quot;Sulsula&quot; — Algeria, Egypt, Sudan
*&quot;Tapinesthis&quot; — Europe
*&quot;Telchius&quot; — Algeria, Morocco, South Africa
*&quot;Termitoonops&quot; — Congo
*&quot;Tinadysderina&quot; 
*&quot;Tolegnaro&quot; 
*&quot;Toloonops&quot; — Mexico
*&quot;Triaeris&quot; — Asia, Africa, Australia
*&quot;Tridysderina&quot; 
*&quot;Trilacuna&quot; — Asia
*&quot;Unicorn&quot; — Argentina, Chile, Bolivia
*&quot;Varioonops&quot; — Central America, South America
*&quot;Vientianea&quot; — Laos
*&quot;Volborattella&quot; 
*&quot;Wanops&quot; — Mexico
*&quot;Xestaspis&quot; — Asia, Oceania, Africa
*&quot;Xiombarg&quot; — Brazil, Argentina
*&quot;Xyccarph&quot; — Brazil
*&quot;Xyphinus&quot; — Asia, Australia
*&quot;Yumates&quot; — Mexico
*&quot;Zyngoonops&quot; — Congo
=== Extinct genera ===

* †&quot;Burmorchestina&quot; Wunderlich 2008 Burmese amber, Myanmar, Cenomanian
* †&quot;Canadaorchestina&quot; Wunderlich 2008 Canadian amber, Campanian
* †&quot;Fossilopaea&quot; Wunderlich 1988 Dominican amber, Miocene

